  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Each day the hotel offers guests a continental breakfast with sweet treats and organic delights, many of which are homemade. Dinner take place in a private dining area next to the bar, so perfect if you get carried away chatting or listening to the live après acts. Most nights you can enjoy a lovely three-course meal but the themed nights come with an additional course and occasionally take place in the basement 'Speak Easy' wine bar.</p>
<p>While you do need to pay for all drinks locally, we highly recommend taking advantage of the hotels comprehensive wine collection at dinner. With over 200 labels to choose from, the staff are more than happy to help you select the right tipple to compliment the menu. </p>
<p>Planning to stay over New Year? Don't worry, the festive meal is included in the cost of your holiday.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
