  <description><![CDATA[<p>With an unbeatable location at the foot of the piste in <a data-udi="umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda}" title="Cervinia">Cervinia</a>, the Hotel Dragon is a great choice for your next ski holiday. The hotel has recently had a sophisticated full make-over.</p>
<h2>Lively Wine Bar</h2>
<p>The bar and lounge have been transformed into a lovely authentic wine bar with the use of warm alpine materials. Sign up locally and put the taste buds to work as you indulge in a selection of carefully selected wines in a tasting to remember.  </p>
<p>Our favourite location is the outdoor terrace. During the sunnier weeks of the season it becomes a suntrap with some of the best views of the Matterhorn from the Italian side of the mountain. The hotel has a lively apr<span>ès scene and a </span>live DJ from 16:00-18:30 every day, there is no better place to enjoy a cool refreshment.</p>
<h2>Location</h2>
<p>There's plenty of shops, bars and restaurants close by and it's just a short 150 metre walk through the snow to the Cretaz lift. Getting back to the hotel is even easier as you can ski all the way to the road opposite the hotel (weather permitting) - that's if you can resist stopping at one of the many bars that line the bottom of the slopes next to the lift.</p>
<h2>Newly Renovated</h2>
<p>Along with the common areas, the bedrooms have had some TLC and provide a spacious and comfortable base for your stay.</p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Dragon the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>
<h3>Why is this an Inghams' Choice property?</h3>
<p><strong>Location</strong> - Make the most of your time in the Cervinia with easy access to the lifts just 150 metres from the Hotel Dragon.</p>
<p><strong>Handpicked</strong> - We love the locally sourced food offered at the Hotel Dragon and the personal service you will find here.</p>
<p><strong>Something extra</strong> - The newly renovated wine bar is a great place to enjoy some après ski, or get lively at one of the hotel's DJ sets.</p>]]></description>
